DESIGNERS’ NOTES
This lounge chair is a sleek and sculptural masterpiece, crafted from high-quality stainless steel with a mirror-polished finish. The polished steel not only gleams with a dramatic shine but also mirrors its surroundings, creating mesmerizing illusions that enhance any space it's placed in. Its seamless,... Read More

This lounge chair is a sleek and sculptural masterpiece, crafted from high-quality stainless steel with a mirror-polished finish. The polished steel not only gleams with a dramatic shine but also mirrors its surroundings, creating mesmerizing illusions that enhance any space it's placed in. Its seamless, curvaceous form flows effortlessly from the rounded base to the top of the backrest, giving it a fluid and modern aesthetic.

The chair's modular design adds versatility, allowing multiple units to be arranged in creative configurations, either in a line or back-to-back, to form larger, eye-catching shapes. Whether used in a commercial setting or a residential space, this lounge chair is a striking statement piece. Its durable stainless steel construction makes it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, blending luxury with functionality to elevate any environment.

SHIPPING & RETURNS

We deliver within the continental United States & Canada. Please request a quotation for Alaska and Hawaii.

Ground Shipping

-Most in-stock items will ship via UPS Ground within 3–5 business days unless otherwise stated on the product page, please refer to the individual product pages for specific processing/lead times.

Please find the full Shipping & Delivery policy with Shipping cost breakdown from our FAQ page and more detail on our Returns & Exchanges page.

Delivery Options

We strongly recommend adding White glove delivery at checkout for large furniture items such as Sideboards, Cabinets, Dining tables, etc. These oversized items ship by freight carrier and are usually palletized to avoid shipping damages.

For such oversized items, if you live in an apartment building or have other entry access challenges, we strongly suggest upgrading to White Glove Delivery

Your order might ship via pallet with a third-party freight company to ensure its safe arrival. Standard shipping includes delivery to your doorstep.

Read full information about Oversized shipments here

Should you discover a manufacturer defect or damage upon delivery, please notify us immediately by email support@foromshop.com or at (844)-757-1224.

TEAR SHEET

ABOUT THE DESIGNER

FOROM

Our approach highlights the balance of tradition, innovation, and sustainability. It captures the emotional essence of our furniture and the thoughtful design behind each piece. We blend the timeless soul of great design with forward-thinking innovation, creating furniture that evokes both history and modernity. Our pieces embody the spirit of craftsmanship while embracing the needs of today’s world, offering a balance of subtle elegance and bold presence that brings a moody, old-soul charm to any space.

Whether curated from our international brand partners or crafted through our own Forom creations, all of our products share a common foundation: a commitment to quality, ethical craftsmanship, and sustainability. We work closely with small, family-owned manufacturers who reflect these values, ensuring that every piece is made with care and integrity.

Our growing circle of skilled artisans and designers from around the world plays an essential role in bringing our vision to life. Each partnership is built on mutual respect and dedication, with every expert contributing their craft to refine and perfect our furniture. The result is a collection that not only captivates with its aesthetics but also stands the test of time, seamlessly blending tradition with modern functionality.

"Take a seat, embrace the future while honoring the past"
